title: Lauren Kenzy vs. à-bas-le-ciel, the podcast nobody asked for! ;-)
description:
This is a conversation with Lauren Kenzy, formerly a.k.a. Lauryn Phoenix (formerly a.k.a. "The Vegan Lass").

Pay the $1 per month to join my Patreon, and, uh, "save the planet", or at least support podcasts like this one (the whole thing is 90 minutes long): https://www.patreon.com/a_bas_le_ciel

The whole conversation is, now, available on this same youtube channel, here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q6ff_3vuv7Y
